				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Bardtail is not online. Last active: 11/30/2004 10:57:30 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Bardtail">Bardtail</a><br></td>
